txt.en:
'Me no likes eagles.

'Eagles go...on dead troll.

'You kill eagles, take feathers.

'Make me like you.'
'No more fouling dead troll...eagle-bird!'\n\nThe troll eats the feathers. Peculiar.
Taskmaster Izubuzri communicated that he wants proof that you killed many eagles. Apparently the eagles are too free with where they perch.
Return to Taskmaster Izubuzri at the Isendeep Mine

Eagles can be found throughout the Coldfells and in a small section of Arador's End to the south of the Isendeep Mine.\n\nTaskmaster Izubuzri wants you to return eagle feathers to him to prove that you have slaughtered a good number of the birds.
